SIMPLE: master_vibrator
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Master vibrator
<hw>Mas"ter vi"bra*tor</hw>. <def>In an internal-combustion engine with
two or more cylinders, an induction coil and vibrator placed in the
circuit between the battery or magneto and the coils for the different
cylinders, which are used without vibrators of their own.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Masterwort</ent>⟦br⟧
